  "title": "Human Resources Executive (HR) Talent Acquisition ML6",
  "description": "<p>Gross Salary:<strong> $2,800 to $5,000+</strong></p><p>Working Days: <strong>Monday to Friday</strong></p><p>Working Hours: <strong>8.30am to 6.00pm</strong></p><p>Location: <strong>Jurong East</strong> (walking distance from Jurong East MRT)<br /><br />We're looking for more passionate individuals to join our team as <strong>HR Talent Acquisition Executives!</strong></p><p>If you're driven, eager to make an impact, and ready to shape the future of companies by connecting companies with top talent, we welcome you to join us!<br /><br /><em><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Engage in full recruitment cycle—sourcing, screening, interviewing, and onboarding top talents</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with Recruitment Managers to ensure recruitment timelines for clients are met</p></li><li><p>Provide clients with exceptional service by fulfilling their staffing needs</p></li><li><p>Work closely with internal Business Development Team to understand recruitment needs of our clients</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree (in any disciple) from recognized institutions</p></li><li><p><strong>No prior experience required—we’ll provide the training you need to succeed!</strong></p></li><li><p>A passion for recruitment and people</p></li><li><p>A friendly and outgoing personality with a strong desire to help others succeed</p></li><li><p>Self-driven, great problem solving skills, attention to detail and willing to learn</p></li></ul><p>Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities.</p><p><br />Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the APPLY NOW BUTTON. </p><p><br />By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by the company relating to this job application.</p><p>https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</p><p><br />**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><br /><br />Michelle Low Shi Hui<br />CEI Registration Number: R25154204<br />EA Licence No: 06C2859 (MCI Career Services Pte Ltd)</p>",
